This paper deals with the task of detecting relevant tweets in crisis situations, which involves natural language processing and information retrieval. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of machine learning models for this task, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). The paper also mentions the use of social media data, which could be relevant to cs.CY (Computers and Society) or cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
